 democratic model with the leftist agenda in retreat fukuyama calls for a new narrative to guide the future of history html+ read more foreign affairs the future of history http www foreignaffairs com artic search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages news of interest stanford democracy experts examine asia middle east february 1 2012 cddrl fsi stanford governance project in the news fukuyama debuts latest book to stanford community april 20 2011 cddrl news is china next will the protests that have swept the middle east inspire a similar movement in china or is that country's middle class more interested in the material than the political francis fukuyama the wall street journal on march 12 2011 francis fukuyama discusses the post washington consensus march 1 2011 fsi stanford cddrl news mcfaul gives class day lecture to 6000 stanford graduates family members june 18 2007 cddrl fsi stanford news second class of stanford summer fellows on democracy and development completes three week symposium august 14 2006 cddrl draper hills summer fellows program news support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
